high_descs: Turn to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Walk to your left and face the stove.
Place the knife in the pot on the back right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Turn around, then walk to the sink on your left.
Place the pot in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it in a sink.

high_descs: Move to the right of the stove by the knife with the yellow handle on top of the counter
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle
Move to face the stove top to the left
Place the knife in the pot on the back right burner on top of the stove
Pick up the pot with the knife in it
Place the pot inside of the sink
Place the pot in the sink
anns.task_desc: Carry a pot with a knife to the sink

high_descs: Turn to your right move forward then turn left facing the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter beside the apple
Turn to your left move forward then face the stove on your right
Put the knife in the pot
Pick up the pot with knife
Turn to your right and head to the sink
Put the pot with knife in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put pot with knife in the sink
